A minimalistic illustration featuring three overlapping translucent circles in red, yellow, and green against a clean white background, with smaller circles in black, blue, and white floating nearby. Thin geometric lines connect various circles showing relationships and intersections between them. The composition uses a limited color palette with subtle shadows creating depth. Some circles overlap perfectly while others only partially intersect or remain completely separate, creating a visual diagram of set relationships. The style is clean, modern, and mathematical with a slight paper texture.
